Included files in tarball:
lab0.c: source code for the project
Makefile: contains make check, default, dist, and clean 
README: readme file with all information in this file
test.sh: Script that runs the smoke tests.
backtrace.png and breakpoint.png: required photos of gdb stacktrace and breakpoint information

Smoke Test Cases

1a) Testing the reading and writing from and to file respectively works without error
1b) Confirm that the input file and output file are identical.
2)  Confirm that the program catches invalid arguments
3)  Confirm that the program catches invalid files names.
4)  Confirm that the program catches errors where we cannot write to file.
5) 	Confrim that the program catches errors where we cannot read from file.
6)  Confirm that the program catches the segmentation fault correctly.

